4f16b05d-1b35-4a36-bd68-62bca9eeb53a.do_description: To make the output, you have to... alternate to the RIGHT of the colored tile with light grey and the original color UNTIL it reaches the rightmost side of the grid, REPEAT this for each applicable colored tile.
4f16b05d-1b35-4a36-bd68-62bca9eeb53a.grid_description: The output grid size... remains the same as the input grid.
4f16b05d-1b35-4a36-bd68-62bca9eeb53a.see_description: In the input, you should see... a grid with randomly placed colored tiles

85a73699-1805-4c9d-8042-0f769905e425.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the input grid. Then, to the right of the first colored block, place a gray block. After the gray block, continue to the right and place a block of the original color. Continue the pattern of original color followed by gray until you reach the right side. Do this with each original colored block.
85a73699-1805-4c9d-8042-0f769905e425.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same as the input grid.
85a73699-1805-4c9d-8042-0f769905e425.see_description: In the input, you should see...one or more single blocks on a black grid.

c385c7fb-7db8-4af9-b9fe-9ed88ae89a1c.do_description: To make the output, you have to...start at the right of the colored block and move left to right alternating the color shown and gray until you get to the edge of the grid on the right. Repeat for each color shown on the grid.
c385c7fb-7db8-4af9-b9fe-9ed88ae89a1c.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same as the input grid.
c385c7fb-7db8-4af9-b9fe-9ed88ae89a1c.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid with some colored blocks.
